  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  65 years +

          -  community-dwelling

          -  residents of Metro Vancouver

          -  recent history (within 12 months) of femoral fracture

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  unable to ambulate 10 meters prior to the femoral fracture were(with/without a walking
             aid)

          -  discharged to a residential care facility

          -  and/or diagnosed with any type of dementia (Alzheimer's, vascular etc.)
      </textblock>
